{"tid":831740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一個月打牌輸80萬人仔　女老闆裝Cam揭騙局","createTime":"2018-09-22T08:11:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T14:35:36.000Z","uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e17044562f6c0adc67989776580b3b777aac4bc5","tid":831740,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T08:11:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20180922/photo/bkn-20180922013222065-0922_00952_001_01p.jpg?20180922013339\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20180922%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180922013222065-0922_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20180922013339&h=465d9369&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n受害人通過安裝閉路電視，揭發騙徒「打龍通」呃錢。圖文無關。（互聯網）<br />\n浙江溫州市一名經營機械廠的女老闆阿西，平日愛好攻打「四方城」，惟早前在短短一個月內輸掉約80萬元（人民幣．下同，約91萬港元）後，深覺情況有異，於是在「雀房」內安裝閉路電視，始揭發原來遭「雀友」詐騙。阿西報案後，4名涉案疑犯因涉嫌詐騙已被警方依法刑事拘留。<br />\n<br />\n阿西表示，2017年打牌時認識一名葉姓男子，2人隨後成為「雀友」。今年3月開始，葉某每星期都會邀請阿西打牌2、3次，但阿西因「手氣差」每次輸掉5萬元（約5.7萬港元）至10萬元（約11.4萬港元）不等。<br />\n<br />\n在短短一個月間輸掉約80萬元後，阿西覺得情況可疑，於是在平日打牌的辦公室內竊裝閉路電視，並在上月邀請葉某「組局」。當晚葉某找來呂某、戴某及金某打牌，期間阿西借口處理工作，着葉某代打，並言明輸贏均由她承擔便離開，最終當晚阿西輸掉8萬元（約9.1萬港元）。阿西隨後通過翻看閉路電視，揭發葉某等4人「打龍通」騙財，在討回被騙金錢不果後報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n警方調查後將葉某等4人拘捕，面對問話，4人對詐騙一事供認不諱。葉某供稱，<span style=\"color: red;\">他們在打牌期間通過觸摸不同的五官部位，伴以隱蔽的暗語，告知同夥叫糊的是甚麼牌</span>；另戴某交代，葉某着其參與其中，不管輸贏都給他20%的利潤提成。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20180922/bkn-20180922013222065-0922_00952_001.html?refer=hn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20180922%2Fbkn-20180922013222065-0922_00952_001.html%3Frefer%3Dhn&d=8p5wVFk5uVpaK%2FyZ%2FVU1JcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=82dbc2fb\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20180922/bkn-20180922013222065-0922_00952_001.html?refer=hn</a>"},{"pid":"c79dfacadeeca8d8151a3231ccbb9d4d0167b8b5","tid":831740,"uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T08:12:12.000Z","msg":"橋唔怕舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c8d5abde0af153498f3a1851438e7f2afa0a7f4","tid":831740,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T08:14:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3661512e57acdf4eca1663c68bb38fc5c8d6679a","tid":831740,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T08:15:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"67524742059808005dfa8cb361322db51c6591c0","tid":831740,"uid":157841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3661512e57acdf4eca1663c68bb38fc5c8d6679a","tid":831740,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9c8d5abde0af153498f3a1851438e7f2afa0a7f4","tid":831740,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T08:14:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T08:15:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T08:18:38.000Z","msg":"以為你想要八筒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cdc2aee921c6deb01d8995f812c6428efe5eb0f","tid":831740,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T08:19:28.000Z","msg":"一個月太狼啦"},{"pid":"4fae17f76202c2957184e3500ae8a8020aeda488","tid":831740,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T08:21:59.000Z","msg":"無啦啦點會有粒飯喺度？"},{"pid":"4a68c3f607b216bb4ddb18b8c7c18513bd256504","tid":831740,"uid":3914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fae17f76202c2957184e3500ae8a8020aeda488","tid":831740,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T08:21:59.000Z","msg":"無啦啦點會有粒飯喺度？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T08:23:18.000Z","msg":"仲熱嘅tim"},{"pid":"8a6f98cf28ffbcf94fbfae104dde120351a89668","tid":831740,"uid":21493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a68c3f607b216bb4ddb18b8c7c18513bd256504","tid":831740,"uid":3914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fae17f76202c2957184e3500ae8a8020aeda488","tid":831740,"uid":51920,"like":0,